Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這感覺真是久違了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.13,0:07:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在是處在意識改變狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別被自己的心給吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就擔心自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出擊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是騎兵型…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天照 誘敵成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防護罩展開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰場形成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜部隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迅速殲滅敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.ⅩⅢ的機架沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(654,655)}cage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機體沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我眼前的是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼犯睏 一坐上法芙娜就會清醒…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是讓我待著別下去麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那裡 是咲良前輩的Mk.Ⅲ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師真的和我們一起戰鬥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無人機…能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人已散開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全體 準備迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在海裡同化能力會減半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要同化島 就只能從天上著手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了上這裡的戰場 你們沒別的選擇 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良 別激動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可要專注支援
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜部隊 開始交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機庫方面報告 Mk.ⅩⅢ的啟動出現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法出擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是還沒理解力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等這股力量覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受祝福 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了島和世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新開始啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是哪裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Sein？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新開始啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島本島被攻擊了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在記錄數據？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯示當前時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和剛才的時間有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 時間恢復了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間 不同的時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯示記錄數據一覽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是之後的 未來的時間…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,(part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺像是有好幾個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算少了哪一個都還有下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意識改變狀態發生了變化？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一部騎兵型嚴重毀壞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共7部正在運作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7部？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎兵型應該只有4部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數據出現錯誤 立刻開始修復
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎兵型共計12部…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良理解了力量 史彥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是超次元現象…Mk.Ⅲ的SDP嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機體變多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很熱 卻覺得冷 好像快凍住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良 振作一點！咲良！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多個自己 到底哪一個才是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現異常！停止系統！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齊格飛系統負責人要求停止系統
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷普尼爾系統負責人出現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能害怕犧牲 史彥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說犧牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系統保持啟動 集中精力消滅敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告系統負責人 將控制進程移交CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣應該能減輕一些負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 我在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！全機更新位置！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.ⅩⅢ還沒好嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員啟動了機架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.ⅩⅢ出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的時間是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告系統 要求變更作戰內容
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰場外有敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2重力波防護罩很快就會被攻破
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更新天照和十字陣形的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素盞嗚尊 轉移部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉移…我來轉移大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以做到 放手去幹！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解釋清楚 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡交給我和Mk.Ⅲ對付
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 保護島上的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們所有人應該都是為此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才存在於此時此地的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道做不做得到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我會試試的！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（OP插入）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是慶樹島…真的轉移了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的…辦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零央！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人已突破第2重力波防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內部防護罩來不及展開！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是從哪裡出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2重力波防護罩附近確認到敵方力場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人陸續實體化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們瞞過了所羅門 究竟是怎麼做到的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊重設戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十字陣形 就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天照 破壞敵方力場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農老師說得沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要是害怕 就保護不了任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕一閃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵方力場消滅 全機上前！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一點了 我馬上就結束這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 相信機體和自己 放手去戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼快 她知道敵人會怎麼行動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.ⅩⅢ 消滅彥島上的半數敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度與Mk.Sein不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎兵型繼續增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共26部於坐標（34,06）展開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是駕駛員們的意志嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們此刻在這裡不能鼓起勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島就沒有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你不同於皆城乙姬的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顯示從現在起10分鐘內的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一時刻的記錄有三條…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是未來不止一個 讓我從中選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊給我消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給他最後一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認彥島 慶樹島上的敵人已被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,增殖的騎兵型也在逐漸消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿撒謝爾型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他無法理解島的力量而發怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不清對方的名堂這點是彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在敵人因憤怒而攻來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下就到達第七個營地了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偵察隊已經出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是正在準備下一個營地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動速度快了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這樣一來保護的難度也會加大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位將軍在調動部隊的同時也在查探…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的敵人的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種感覺還是揮之不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明用這雙手保護了他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎前輩是不是就能救下他們了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別想了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再自責 他們也不會復生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你還要說走這一趟是值得的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了憎恨產生的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為認識到了自己的無力 所以才會去憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了這種事又能怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你都享受了龍宮島的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們才能不憎恨世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想將我所知道的和平告訴整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我才會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果龍宮島也碰上斯利那加這樣的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信夥伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一定不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:19:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯了 雖然只有和昨天一樣的口糧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直都在待命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一有事就能馬上出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼我去就能救下他們這種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明在斯利那加就死了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去的確就能救下他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能像你這樣一直駕駛法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以害你一直勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並沒有勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎麼不都死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…Festum嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:20:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點加入我們嘛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:22:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令 遠見醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍司 咲良！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅸ…里奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你將會懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.86,0:23:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並非因絕望而產生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.78,0:23:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在與命運的對抗中找到的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:24:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫使我們付出犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:11.13,titlenx,,0,0,0,,尋求破曉的行進
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,蒼穹的法芙娜 EXODUS 第十四回
